;s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:366:\"<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/800k-wordpress-sites-are-now-backed-up-by-updraftplus/\">800k WordPress sites are now backed up by UpdraftPlus!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Abigail Walters-Davies\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1962:\"<div class=\"et_pb_section  et_pb_section_0 et_section_regular\">\n				\n				\n					\n					<div class=\" et_pb_row et_pb_row_0\">\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_0\">\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_0\">\n				\n<p>It’s taken just 92 days to hit this new milestone – 8 days less than the last.</p>\n<p>In the last 24 hours the powers that be at <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/\">WordPress.org</a> has indicated that our UpdraftPlus community has grown by another 100,000. UpdraftPlus now actively backs up over<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/\"> 800,000 WordPress sites</a>.</p>\n<p>We also surpassed over 5 million downloads &#8211; that&#8217;s the population of Norway!</p>\n<p>This makes us the 26<sup>th</sup> most-installed WordPress plugin on <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/browse/popular/\">WordPress.org</a> and the highest ranking WordPress backup plugin. With a rating of 4.9 stars we are very appreciative of being able to call ourselves the world&#8217;s most trusted backup plugin.</p>\n<p>Thank you to all our users that help get UpdraftPlus to this position. WordPress is a great community that we’re proud to be part of. We’re excited to still be on track to back up 1 million sites by the end of 2016, so stay tuned for out next big milestone update.</p>\n\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->\n					\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->\n				\n			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section -->\n<span class=\"et_bloom_bottom_trigger\"></span><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/800k-wordpress-sites-are-now-backed-up-by-updraftplus/\">800k WordPress sites are now backed up by UpdraftPlus!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://updraftplus.com/800k-wordpress-sites-are-now-backed-up-by-updraftplus/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://updraftplus.com/800k-wordpress-sites-are-now-backed-up-by-updraftplus/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n