17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:750:\"<p>In the latter part of 2015, Amazon introduced a new storage class option for their S3 storage cloud &#8211; &#8220;standard &#8211; infrequent access&#8221;; a storage class which can bring significant cost savings (as long as you can live with your &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/amazon-s3-infrequent-access-storage-class/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/amazon-s3-infrequent-access-storage-class/\">Amazon S3 &#8211; infrequent access storage class</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"udadmin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1782:\"<p>In the latter part of 2015, <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/aws-storage-update-new-lower-cost-s3-storage-option-glacier-price-reduction/\">Amazon introduced a new storage class option for their S3 storage cloud</a> &#8211; &#8220;standard &#8211; infrequent access&#8221;; a storage class which can bring significant cost savings (as long as you can live with your data not be reachable 0.1% of the time &#8211; but with no loss in long-term redundancy of the backup).</p>\n<p>We&#8217;re pleased to announce that the next release of <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/shop/updraftplus-premium/\">UpdraftPlus Premium</a> will support this storage class, alongside the existing &#8220;standard&#8221; and &#8220;reduced redundancy&#8221; options; i.e. you can now choose from each of these 3 classes.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-154692\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/s3opts.png\" alt=\"S3 enhanced options\" width=\"666\" height=\"380\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/s3opts.png 666w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/s3opts-300x171.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/s3opts-510x291.png 510w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/s3opts-610x348.png 610w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px\" /></p>\n<p>David Anderson (lead developer, UpdraftPlus)</p>\n<span class=\"et_bloom_bottom_trigger\"></span><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/amazon-s3-infrequent-access-storage-class/\">Amazon S3 &#8211; infrequent access storage class</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://updraftplus.com/amazon-s3-infrequent-access-storage-class/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:4:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"Copy.Com – going, gone\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.co